Title: Product Integral Formalism and Non-Abelian Stokes Theorem
Authors: Robert L. Karp, Freydoon Mansouri, Jung S. Rno
Comments: Latex; condensed version of hep-th/9903221, to appear in Jour. Math.
  Phys
Report-no: uctp117.99
Journal-ref: J.Math.Phys. 40 (1999) 6033-6043
\\
  We make use of the properties of product integrals to obtain a surface
product integral representation for the Wilson loop operator. The result can be
interpreted as the non-abelian version of Stokes' theorem.
